opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 2nd day of November, 2011, the Application for Leave to File Original Process is GRANTED, and the Petition for Writ of Habeas Corpus and the Motion for an Evidentiary Hearing are DENIED.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
